{"tid":1614664,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個地圖有齊哂美心富臨既舖頭","createTime":"2019-10-03T00:46:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T11:44:54.000Z","uid":104648,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"edfcc17e6c1ef16ab9577da0d74105e8e912ff7e","tid":1614664,"uid":104648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T00:46:36.000Z","msg":"有鑑香港人呢幾日對美心富臨既熱情，有班傻仔尋晚通頂入哂所有呢兩個集團既舖頭落個MAP到，SEARCH美心/富臨就可以SHOW哂出黎！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://neoguidehk.com/map/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fneoguidehk.com%2Fmap%2F&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7OSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=5e9388c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://neoguidehk.com/map/</a><br />\n <br />\n佢地既舖頭真係總有一間係左近，隨時隨地都可以慰藉香港人既心靈<br />\n- 行過千兩元氣呢啲人氣壽司店，梗係要瘋狂禁飛啦，GULU電話攞飛又得，入去可以免費無限飲綠茶食薑，坐足全日<br />\n- 美心皇宮係少數仲有推車仔既酒樓，咁有特色一定要每個星期六日最繁忙既早茶時段用GULU攞飛見識下<br />\n- 壓力大？美心西餅/東海堂啲包係好好既STRESS BALL，記得要俾左錢先呀，如果唔係個包就無人買架啦  <br />\n- 當然仲有好多野玩啦，但係玩時玩，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">落大雨果陣記得開遮</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n重溫一下佢地既威水史<br />\n【逃犯條例】何超瓊伍淑清將在聯合國演講：暴力示威破壞平和生活<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時中國/373555/逃犯條例-何超瓊伍淑清將在聯合國演講-暴力示威破壞平和生活\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%2F373555%2F%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E4%BD%95%E8%B6%85%E7%93%8A%E4%BC%8D%E6%B7%91%E6%B8%85%E5%B0%87%E5%9C%A8%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E5%9C%8B%E6%BC%94%E8%AC%9B-%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E7%A0%B4%E5%A3%9E%E5%B9%B3%E5%92%8C%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7OSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=f4f89331\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時中國/373555/逃犯條例-何超瓊伍淑清將在聯合國演講-暴力示威破壞平和生活</a><br />\n【逆權運動】罷課風波 美心大小姐好無面<br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_691910_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_691910_0&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7OSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=9e65f2f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_691910_0&h=6681589b\" target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_691910_0</a><br />\n【逆權運動】北角富臨聚集福建幫 網民籲罷食 富臨：白衣人酒樓內冇違法<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190812/59922630\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190812%2F59922630&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7OSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=a27c6ea9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190812%2F59922630&h=aae6b18d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190812/59922630</a><br />\n【8.11 北角】黑衫青年行經富臨皇宮被五漢圍毆 立場記者被揮棒指嚇 港台記者遇襲 在場警員無拉人<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/8-11-北角-黑衫青年行經富臨皇宮被五漢圍毆-立場記者被指嚇搶腳架-港台記者遇襲-在場警員無拉人/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F8-11-%E5%8C%97%E8%A7%92-%E9%BB%91%E8%A1%AB%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E8%A1%8C%E7%B6%93%E5%AF%8C%E8%87%A8%E7%9A%87%E5%AE%AE%E8%A2%AB%E4%BA%94%E6%BC%A2%E5%9C%8D%E6%AF%86-%E7%AB%8B%E5%A0%B4%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E5%9A%87%E6%90%B6%E8%85%B3%E6%9E%B6-%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%B0%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-%E5%9C%A8%E5%A0%B4%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E7%84%A1%E6%8B%89%E4%BA%BA%2F&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7OSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=1afa237c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F8-11-%E5%8C%97%E8%A7%92-%E9%BB%91%E8%A1%AB%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E8%A1%8C%E7%B6%93%E5%AF%8C%E8%87%A8%E7%9A%87%E5%AE%AE%E8%A2%AB%E4%BA%94%E6%BC%A2%E5%9C%8D%E6%AF%86-%E7%AB%8B%E5%A0%B4%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E5%9A%87%E6%90%B6%E8%85%B3%E6%9E%B6-%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%B0%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-%E5%9C%A8%E5%A0%B4%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E7%84%A1%E6%8B%89%E4%BA%BA%2F&h=24790ee9\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/8-11-北角-黑衫青年行經富臨皇宮被五漢圍毆-立場記者被指嚇搶腳架-港台記者遇襲-在場警員無拉人/</a><br />\n<br />\n講完美心/富臨，呢個MAP仲有超多唔同既黃店，藍店同埋中資，仲會每日更新。所有黃店都經過有嚴格既FACT CHECK，等緊大家去瘋狂懲罰。藍店同中資都要認清楚&mdash; &mdash; 中蟈既硬&quot;實力&quot;除左解放軍同埋黑警之外，就係充斥住香港既呢啲中資/無良企業，我地一定要斷佢米路，呢個係和理非既戰場， 係勇武既戰場 ，係所有香港人既戰場！加油！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5877e69dc3403190efcf62c0bbe7b1b8664c9d2e","tid":1614664,"uid":104648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T00:49:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"67a0d0a0f96dc69480bae1fd1ea8c002cf58bbfc","tid":1614664,"uid":104648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T00:49:56.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"316d936d80a1697a00a6532574200da61eb97158","tid":1614664,"uid":104648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T00:52:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a8b16b92ace2531cb8aa15051fdd1cf1f272e6c1","tid":1614664,"uid":79589,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T00:53:11.000Z","msg":"去左探望受傷嘅Starbuck<br />\n<br />\n做法唔完美，可接受，有改善空間<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Starbuck  最貴、最有價值係部咖啡機，廿幾三十萬</span></span><br />\n<br />\n扑爛左就冇得開，訂都要時間"},{"pid":"a23fb174ad72dea732e6383d1a3cfeb765c148b6","tid":1614664,"uid":104648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8b16b92ace2531cb8aa15051fdd1cf1f272e6c1","tid":1614664,"uid":79589,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T00:53:11.000Z","msg":"去左探望受傷嘅Starbuck<br />\n<br />\n做法唔完美，可接受，有改善空間<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Starbuck  最貴、最有價值係部咖啡機，廿幾三十萬</span></span><br />\n<br />\n扑爛左就冇得開，訂都要時間"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T00:56:33.000Z","msg":"如果去水位爆左，水喉長開會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/